query: SELECT s.device_id, date_trunc($1, collected_at) "collected_at!: NaiveDateTime", CAST(sum(download_diff) AS bigint) "download!", CAST(sum(upload_diff) AS bigint) "upload!" FROM vpn_session_stats INNER JOIN vpn_client_session s ON session_id = s.id WHERE s.device_id = ANY($2) AND collected_at >= $3 AND s.location_id = $4  GROUP BY device_id, collected_at ORDER BY device_id, collected_at
